import { TimeLocaleDefinition } from 'd3-time-format';

export const DEFAULT_D3_TIME_FORMAT: TimeLocaleDefinition = {
  dateTime: '%x, %X',
  date: '%-m/%-d/%Y',
  time: '%-I:%M:%S %p',
  periods: ['AM', 'PM'],
  days: [
    'Sunday',
    'Monday',
    'Tuesday',
    'Wednesday',
    'Thursday',
    'Friday',
    'Saturday',
  ],
  shortDays: ['Sun', 'Mon', 'Tue', 'Wed', 'Thu', 'Fri', 'Sat'],
  months: [
    'January',
    'February',
    'March',
    'April',
    'May',
    'June',
    'July',
    'August',
    'September',
    'October',
    'November',
    'December',
  ],
  shortMonths: [
    'Jan',
    'Feb',
    'Mar',
    'Apr',
    'May',
    'Jun',
    'Jul',
    'Aug',
    'Sep',
    'Oct',
    'Nov',
    'Dec',
  ],
};
